Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.24,0:00:02.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,《超感警探》前情提要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.70,0:00:06.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她說血腥約翰左肩膀有個紋身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.35,0:00:07.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三個點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.82,0:00:09.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我的籌碼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.51,0:00:12.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把五名疑犯同時
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.24,0:00:13.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集合到一個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.18,0:00:15.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后再檢查是否有紋身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.10,0:00:16.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何才能做到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.17,0:00:18.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-周四晚上八點見面  -好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.93,0:00:20.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周四晚上八點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.50,0:00:22.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我需要你的幫助  -沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.77,0:00:25.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你如果不去  他就會認為你是血腥約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.30,0:00:27.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我如果去了  你和簡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.88,0:00:29.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不會再懷疑我是血腥約翰了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.73,0:00:31.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后絕對不會了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.42,0:00:32.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的確定了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.99,0:00:35.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-是的  -此案結束的時候我要在場
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.15,0:00:36.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就等您這句話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.76,0:00:38.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血腥約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.45,0:00:40.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚我若能去見你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.29,0:00:42.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是再高興不過了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.26,0:00:45.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血腥約翰  有個紋身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.12,0:00:51.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左臂上有三個點  就在肩膀上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.97,0:00:53.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們都得
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.56,0:00:55.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.64,0:00:59.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立刻動手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.32,0:01:05.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開始脫吧  快
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.10,0:01:08.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了  脫掉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.38,0:01:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太荒唐了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.05,0:01:23.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.15,0:01:31.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是你想的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.43,0:01:33.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你弄錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.59,0:01:35.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是血腥約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.98,0:01:39.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,派翠克  等等  派翠克
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.10,0:01:40.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看  這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.55,0:01:41.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.71,0:02:00.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.36,0:02:02.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到他們倆那邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.10,0:02:09.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們別動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.34,0:02:11.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  你們三個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.61,0:02:14.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到墻邊站著  快
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.31,0:02:23.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.44,0:03:00.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快叫消防部門和急救人員過來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.01,0:03:01.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴他們這里有多人傷亡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.97,0:03:02.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警戒線拉起來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.88,0:03:03.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  長官
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.52,0:03:05.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-把你的手電筒給我  我進去  -給你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.04,0:03:11.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.75,0:03:14.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.46,0:03:28.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史密斯探員
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.63,0:03:29.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史密斯探員  我是特蕾莎·里斯本
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.85,0:03:32.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你沒事吧  -發生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.06,0:03:34.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這里剛剛發生了爆炸  急救人員已經在路上了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.61,0:03:35.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們會救治你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.75,0:03:41.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不許動  -什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.24,0:03:42.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把手舉起來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.22,0:03:44.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然我就開槍了  快
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.14,0:03:46.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽著  我不明白你在說什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.34,0:03:47.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明顯搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.74,0:04:00.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史密斯往哪邊走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.24,0:04:01.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的天哪  里斯本
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.14,0:04:03.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,頭兒  我們必須得找到史密斯  他是血腥約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.55,0:04:05.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去找人幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.79,0:04:08.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.31,0:04:11.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能聽到我講話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.21,0:04:15.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡  快醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.73,0:04:44.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.83,0:04:45.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.97,0:04:47.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醫生說簡的情況穩定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.30,0:04:49.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒受什么重傷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.93,0:04:51.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他只是醒不過來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.93,0:05:02.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現場發現了三個人的殘骸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.58,0:05:04.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,化驗確認是布萊特·斯特爾斯  雷·哈弗內
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.66,0:05:05.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和托馬斯·麥卡利斯特的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.96,0:05:06.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你確定嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.61,0:05:08.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以為核攻擊都干不掉布萊特·斯特爾斯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.99,0:05:10.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尸體都被燒焦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.91,0:05:13.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但鑒證科還是提取出了DNA
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.14,0:05:15.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驗尸官那邊將結果與醫療記錄進行比對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.03,0:05:16.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已確認三位死者正是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.50,0:05:17.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯特爾斯  哈弗內和麥卡利斯特
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.81,0:05:19.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那史密斯呢  有人看到他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.58,0:05:21.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒  瑞斯比和范佩爾正在查
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.05,0:05:50.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長官
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.32,0:05:52.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就知道在這兒能找到你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.65,0:05:53.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.65,0:05:56.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事  不過我確實得喝杯咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.63,0:05:57.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能幫我去買一杯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.29,0:05:59.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們馬上要開始聯合追捕史密斯了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.76,0:06:01.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你該趕快去抓他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.41,0:06:03.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我更想待在這里  長官
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.45,0:06:04.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你是...  -周和其他組員應付得來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.85,0:06:06.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是要拒絕執行我的命令嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.84,0:06:07.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.10,0:06:09.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想在這里陪他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.14,0:06:10.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你給我聽清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.57,0:06:12.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我命令你現在馬上離開
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:13.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帶領你的組員一起去抓捕史密斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.65,0:06:18.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡  簡  那個呼叫按鈕在哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.93,0:06:20.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去叫護士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.18,0:06:23.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.73,0:06:40.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,頭兒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.62,0:07:11.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們現在認為  是血腥約翰帶去的炸彈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.55,0:07:13.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要殺死簡和其他嫌犯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.12,0:07:13.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  但怎么布下的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.99,0:07:16.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是血腥約翰隨身偷偷帶進去的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.42,0:07:18.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犯罪現場小組從墻上發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.00,0:07:20.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炸彈外殼的碎片  碎片非常小
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:23.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這說明火藥密度高  威力很大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.18,0:07:24.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那肯定不是自制的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.24,0:07:25.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯  我猜是軍用級別的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.53,0:07:26.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就說明我們能夠追蹤到來源
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.90,0:07:29.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些是最有可能的來源
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.66,0:07:31.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查查看最近他們中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.20,0:07:32.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有誰曾報告丟失過炸藥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.49,0:07:33.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  馬上去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.57,0:07:34.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-有線索了嗎  -是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.78,0:07:36.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里斯本在史密斯逃走前曾擊中過他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.85,0:07:38.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是帶著槍傷在四處逃竄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.77,0:07:40.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醫院看到槍傷必須向警方報備
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.49,0:07:41.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以他不能去看急診
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.83,0:07:44.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯  他需要一個不會聲張的醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.57,0:07:45.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史密斯一直在薩克拉門托工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.91,0:07:48.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我查了一下全市他負責過的案件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.42,0:07:49.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他所在的緝毒小組
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.61,0:07:51.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去年在薩克拉門托市南部
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.09,0:07:52.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓捕過阿列克·拉夫羅夫醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.73,0:07:55.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個非法開具奧施康定[強力止痛藥]處方的醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.73,0:07:55.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}Dr. Feelgood指的是常給病人開出興奮劑等安慰性藥方的醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.36,0:07:57.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-然后呢  -案子審判不順利
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.38,0:07:59.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,證物丟失  拉夫羅夫被無罪釋放
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.31,0:08:00.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以史密斯很清楚在哪能找到一位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.83,0:08:01.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會報警的醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.81,0:08:03.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  我們馬上去查
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:14.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是你想的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.14,0:08:16.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是血腥約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.33,0:08:18.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,派翠克  等等  看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.33,0:08:35.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.04,0:08:43.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里斯本
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.60,0:08:47.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你家里發生了爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.58,0:08:50.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我昏迷多久了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.38,0:08:51.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十二個小時
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.40,0:08:55.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里德·史密斯是血腥約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.21,0:08:57.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到他肩膀上的紋身了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.07,0:08:59.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不只他有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.50,0:09:02.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麥卡利斯特身上也有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.43,0:09:05.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他已經死了  斯特爾斯和哈弗內也死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.60,0:09:07.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-還有伯特侖  -伯特侖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.39,0:09:09.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也有那個紋身
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.00,0:09:11.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.20,0:09:13.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他剛才還在這
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.25,0:09:15.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他剛才就站在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.47,0:09:16.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他  他還一直想讓我離開
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.61,0:09:17.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是要殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.99,0:09:20.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我的衣服呢  -別著急  好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.13,0:09:21.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒事  我們沒有時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.57,0:09:22.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡  簡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.83,0:09:24.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的衣服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.95,0:09:28.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是特蕾莎·里斯本
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.20,0:09:29.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在全州境內發出里德·史密斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.97,0:09:32.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和蓋爾·伯特侖的通緝令
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.91,0:09:34.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯  就是伯特侖局長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:36.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接近時務必小心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.63,0:09:38.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們持有武器  十分危險
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.10,0:09:40.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們其中一個就是血腥約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.60,0:09:42.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}伊凡·拉夫羅夫醫生診所
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.50,0:09:43.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}今日停業
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.57,0:09:58.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請趕快離開  女士  警察辦案
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.17,0:10:02.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.67,0:10:05.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.51,0:10:08.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,子彈還在你體內
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.31,0:10:10.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別廢話了  趕緊取出來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.10,0:10:13.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會很疼的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.53,0:10:16.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你確定不吃點止疼藥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.12,0:10:17.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.34,0:10:20.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不吃  我要保持警覺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.81,0:10:21.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就隨你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.38,0:10:25.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.34,0:10:40.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老虎  老虎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.14,0:10:42.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老虎  老虎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.14,0:10:44.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史密斯在這
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.03,0:10:46.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  他快喊破喉嚨了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.15,0:10:48.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不會成為麻煩的  你打算怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.46,0:10:50.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我剛從加調局得到消息
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.23,0:10:52.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有幾個探員正要來這里找史密斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.78,0:10:54.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-那我們該怎么辦  -趕緊了事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.47,0:10:56.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你進去搞定他  加調局的人來了我拖住他們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.22,0:10:58.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.85,0:11:01.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從后面把他帶出去  在那干掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.22,0:11:17.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-他逼我這么做的  我是無辜的  -閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.21,0:11:18.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要他一走我就會報警的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.61,0:11:20.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我不想惹麻煩  -閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.95,0:11:25.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是組織的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.24,0:11:27.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老虎  老虎  你為什么不給我們打電話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.56,0:11:29.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說來真怪  因為我不相信你們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.21,0:11:31.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要信任你的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.25,0:11:33.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是來幫你的  你能走路嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.96,0:11:35.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得給他縫好  不然會失血的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.59,0:11:37.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能走路
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.90,0:11:56.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是科德羅警探  對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.63,0:11:57.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑞斯比探員
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.35,0:11:59.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.00,0:12:02.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是薩城警局的  負責柯克蘭槍擊案
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.27,0:12:04.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這位是格蕾斯·范佩爾探員
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.02,0:12:06.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們怎么來薩城南部了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.47,0:12:08.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們跟一條線索過來抓里德·史密斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.92,0:12:10.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是  血腥約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.57,0:12:12.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來我們快你們一步
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.06,0:12:13.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的人已經進去抓他了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.25,0:12:15.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要我們看住后面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.16,0:12:17.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不用  我們能搞定  -你確定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.78,0:12:21.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我們不是加調局的  但是我們也是警察
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.22,0:12:23.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失陪一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.34,0:12:27.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.48,0:12:28.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑞斯比  你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.74,0:12:31.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在醫生辦公室外面  史密斯好像在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.44,0:12:32.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有警察在你身邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.05,0:12:34.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.19,0:12:35.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  你仔細聽清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.34,0:12:37.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要相信任何一名執法人員
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.13,0:12:40.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰也不能相信  明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.36,0:12:41.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.29,0:12:42.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.10,0:12:46.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們去后面四周看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.93,0:12:47.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.02,0:12:49.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.85,0:12:51.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,車就在這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:53.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都安排好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.48,0:12:56.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在附近有個安全屋  干凈衣服  一名醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.35,0:12:57.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出城的路線也準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.94,0:13:00.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安全屋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.30,0:13:03.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也對某個人說過一次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.45,0:13:06.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎  后來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.65,0:13:09.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我朝他后背開了六槍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.00,0:13:12.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖就范吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.14,0:13:17.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.95,0:13:25.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放下武器
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.97,0:13:37.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.46,0:14:01.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你沒事吧  -沒事  你還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.24,0:14:02.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.17,0:14:10.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史密斯趁亂逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.79,0:14:12.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個警探也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.55,0:14:15.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,頭兒  他們想殺史密斯和我們  這是為什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.54,0:14:16.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我不知道  -看看他的肩膀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.86,0:14:18.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-什么  -讓他看看左肩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.86,0:14:21.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓瑞斯比把他襯衣脫了看他的肩膀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.25,0:14:23.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里斯本想讓你看他的左肩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.59,0:14:29.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.36,0:14:32.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有  他肩上有那個紋身
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.90,0:14:34.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,頭兒  這是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.19,0:14:35.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  把他帶回局里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.00,0:14:36.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別讓任何人接近他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.65,0:14:39.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帶回去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.60,0:14:52.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查到襲擊你們的警察身份了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.37,0:14:54.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我們抓到的那個  保羅·魏海根警官
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.96,0:14:56.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當警察六年  模范警察
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.92,0:14:59.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受過幾次表彰  沒紀律問題
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.40,0:15:01.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那另一個  科德羅警探呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.36,0:15:02.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打電話問了他隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.38,0:15:03.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說他一小時前請了病假
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.75,0:15:05.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是沒查到伯特侖的行蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.08,0:15:06.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就著重調查我們抓到的這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.54,0:15:07.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許簡會弄清真相
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.08,0:15:11.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人派你殺里德·史密斯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.62,0:15:14.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無可奉告
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.99,0:15:16.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你為什么要殺他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.01,0:15:22.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那紋身是怎么回事  有什么意義
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.18,0:15:29.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不善言辭  我懂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.12,0:15:32.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禍從口出嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.51,0:15:34.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,壞消息是  你的表情控制得不夠好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.72,0:15:38.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我們要玩個你演我猜的小游戲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.06,0:15:39.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我告訴你些事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.13,0:15:41.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你用表情告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.59,0:15:43.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是對是錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.48,0:15:44.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有意思嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.19,0:15:47.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你偷過東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.68,0:15:51.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你背著女友偷腥過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.89,0:15:53.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打過她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.51,0:15:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜歡施暴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.31,0:15:57.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我從沒打過女人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.08,0:16:00.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是一個由警察和其他政府官員
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.24,0:16:02.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,組成的秘密組織成員嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.28,0:16:05.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.04,0:16:09.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你為維護那個組織的利益犯過罪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.06,0:16:12.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.14,0:16:16.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史密斯探員也是組織成員
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.06,0:16:19.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.59,0:16:23.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,組織派你去那個診所殺他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.89,0:16:24.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.90,0:16:29.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加調局局長蓋爾·伯特侖也是組織成員
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.88,0:16:32.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.29,0:16:34.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等級太低了對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.87,0:16:38.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里德·史密斯探員是血腥約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.56,0:16:40.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.38,0:16:44.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓋爾·伯特侖是血腥約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.31,0:16:47.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.70,0:16:51.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你肩上的紋身是組織成員的標志
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.69,0:16:55.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道你在說什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.57,0:16:56.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又對了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.37,0:17:00.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有個暗號
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.43,0:17:03.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你們成員間用來識別身份
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.90,0:17:05.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和求救的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.44,0:17:08.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"老虎  老虎"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.52,0:17:12.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從我腦子里滾出去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.52,0:17:15.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個腐敗警察的秘密組織
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.73,0:17:17.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血腥約翰是成員之一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.51,0:17:19.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帕特里奇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.46,0:17:22.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他死之前對我說了"老虎  老虎"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.05,0:17:24.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對  沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.45,0:17:25.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在求救
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.21,0:17:28.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寄希望于你也是成員之一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.37,0:17:29.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果他也有紋身
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.51,0:17:31.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驗尸報告里應該有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.26,0:17:32.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能相信什么報告
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.75,0:17:33.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要親眼看到才行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.75,0:17:35.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會讓周去檢查尸體
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.83,0:17:37.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是很有可能帕特里奇已經下葬了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.67,0:17:39.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就讓周帶上鏟子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.18,0:17:41.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的人在找史密斯  伯特侖在外逃中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.86,0:17:43.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底誰是血腥約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.07,0:17:44.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是伯特侖還是史密斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.56,0:17:48.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要看著他們的眼睛才能確定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.62,0:17:53.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驗尸官兩天前把尸體送過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.21,0:17:55.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-謀殺案被害人是吧  -是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.60,0:17:58.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜就是  所以才會一直留著他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.62,0:18:00.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸好你今天來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.23,0:18:02.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天就什么都看不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.01,0:18:04.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.15,0:18:05.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布雷特·帕特里奇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.44,0:18:06.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幫把手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.46,0:18:28.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.42,0:18:30.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把刀給我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.61,0:18:40.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燒之前都會給他們穿上好衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.37,0:18:41.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道為什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.48,0:18:59.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周發了張照片過來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.50,0:19:06.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說明什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.79,0:19:08.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得這說明什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.54,0:19:16.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史密斯處理好了么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.74,0:19:19.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們差點就在診所那里解決他了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.50,0:19:21.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加調局的人來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.62,0:19:23.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史密斯跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.27,0:19:24.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他可真會跑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.90,0:19:27.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有點事要處理
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.12,0:19:28.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這兒等我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.15,0:19:39.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝  托馬斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.80,0:19:41.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您很久沒來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.09,0:19:42.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很高興見到你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.63,0:20:39.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史密斯現在可能在任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.08,0:20:41.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我試著追蹤他手機上全球定位信號
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.04,0:20:42.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經關閉好幾個小時了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.42,0:20:44.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像他這樣的腐敗聯調局警察一定會有一次性手機
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.77,0:20:46.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉夫羅夫醫生說他還沒縫合史密斯的傷口
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.87,0:20:48.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他現在還帶著槍傷四處走動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.87,0:20:50.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么不管他在哪兒  情況一定不好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.61,0:20:52.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最終一定會被人發現的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.22,0:20:53.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  但是發現他的警察
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.87,0:21:04.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太可怕了  我們誰都不能信
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.73,0:21:07.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.37,0:21:48.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,范佩爾探員
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.60,0:21:49.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得幫幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.76,0:21:50.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史密斯探員
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.10,0:21:52.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們會殺了我的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.94,0:21:53.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要自首
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.98,0:21:54.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.35,0:21:58.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}第十八大道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.81,0:22:01.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在市中心  給周打電話  他應該在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.38,0:22:02.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了  我們這就來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.76,0:22:11.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史密斯聯系加調局了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.59,0:22:13.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他用了組織給他的一次性手機
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.97,0:22:14.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們監聽了那部手機
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.84,0:22:16.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他要自首
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.03,0:22:17.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯  叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.61,0:22:19.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加調局的人去接他了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.41,0:22:21.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可不行  他在哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.09,0:22:23.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,離這兒不遠的小巷子里  我們運氣很不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.85,0:22:24.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他認識你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.92,0:22:26.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不認識  在診所那兒他沒看見我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.85,0:22:29.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  你現在就是加調局探員了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.61,0:22:33.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要一起去嗎  說不定挺好玩兒的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.72,0:22:35.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不去了  我還有別的事要處理
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.67,0:22:37.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-到時再碰頭吧  -行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.12,0:22:38.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次別失手了  行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.13,0:22:41.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  長官
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.80,0:23:34.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里德·史密斯探員
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.28,0:23:37.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在嗎  范佩爾探員派我來的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.16,0:23:46.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.80,0:23:51.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奧斯卡·科德羅探員  加調局的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.01,0:23:53.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來接你回去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.42,0:24:05.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得保證我安全
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.62,0:24:07.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們無處不在
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.56,0:24:10.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.30,0:24:12.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們無處不在
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.57,0:24:15.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天吶
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.31,0:24:16.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到車尾去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.51,0:24:37.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不會真以為你能逃脫得了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.41,0:24:45.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你懂事的  幫個忙  自己爬后備箱里去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.93,0:24:47.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再讓我歇會兒  行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.93,0:24:49.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到后備箱里去歇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.67,0:24:52.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別逼我動手
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.60,0:25:02.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上車
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.57,0:25:15.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有個條件  我要求完全豁免權
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.46,0:25:16.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非你們放過我  否則我一個字都不會說的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.90,0:25:18.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.36,0:25:19.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.94,0:25:21.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站起來走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.41,0:25:24.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過但愿你能在你的朋友追上你之前
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.03,0:25:25.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走出這棟大樓
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.87,0:25:27.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你坦白我們所要的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.92,0:25:30.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我保證把你安排在遠離加州的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.22,0:25:32.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聯邦監獄
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.70,0:25:34.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保證你安全
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.73,0:25:44.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五年前  我傷了背
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.51,0:25:47.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了幫我表兄搬張該死的沙發
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.15,0:25:50.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醫生給我開了點兒止痛片
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.74,0:25:52.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果我欲罷不能
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.42,0:25:54.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我上癮了  自己都沒覺察到
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.44,0:25:55.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.01,0:25:57.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.13,0:26:00.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在卡森泉把一個小混混
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.65,0:26:03.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逼到了一條巷子里  然后我的癮上來了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.26,0:26:05.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全意識不清了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.45,0:26:08.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以為有人跟蹤我
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.83,0:26:14.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我開槍打死了一個小女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.69,0:26:17.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她十二歲
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.29,0:26:21.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當地警察采了我的血樣
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.86,0:26:23.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們有目擊證人  我當時死定了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.78,0:26:26.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后來了個警探
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.74,0:26:28.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他找到我說
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.70,0:26:30.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們可以把這事擺平
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.23,0:26:32.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后真的擺平了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.47,0:26:35.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血樣  目擊證人  都擺平了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.37,0:26:37.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們擺平那事兒以后
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.69,0:26:40.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聯調局還給我頒發了一枚獎章呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.35,0:26:45.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"他們"到底是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.89,0:26:51.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們自稱為"布萊克組織"
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.08,0:26:52.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什么
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.63,0:26:54.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"老虎  老虎"
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.88,0:26:58.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"老虎  老虎  燃燒著煌煌的火光"
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.88,0:26:58.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}此處摘自郭沫若譯本
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.60,0:27:02.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來自布萊克的詩作
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.25,0:27:06.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概某人很喜歡他的作品吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.38,0:27:08.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,組織里還有些什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.13,0:27:10.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警察  法官  聯調局探員
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.30,0:27:12.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任何一個有秘密需要掩蓋的執法人員
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.98,0:27:14.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如你的毒癮
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.77,0:27:18.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當你有麻煩了  向他們求助
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.32,0:27:20.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當他們讓你做點什么  你就得照做
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.25,0:27:21.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"老虎  老虎"
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.96,0:27:23.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.66,0:27:26.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,組織有頭目嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.13,0:27:29.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定有
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.86,0:27:31.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我不知道是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.74,0:27:33.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只知道我所接觸的小團體
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.56,0:27:36.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我猜測
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.71,0:27:39.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整個組織至少有數百人  甚至上千人
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.42,0:27:41.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道就沒人發覺這一切嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.38,0:27:45.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鮑勃·柯克蘭知道這事  對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.71,0:27:51.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快直接招了吧  說出來給你自己一個解脫
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.21,0:27:55.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.84,0:27:57.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他知道的太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.05,0:27:59.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我殺了他
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.92,0:28:03.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道血腥約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.23,0:28:05.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是布萊克組織的成員嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.62,0:28:17.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你確定嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.86,0:28:20.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血腥約翰有一個追隨者
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.30,0:28:22.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麗貝卡·安德森
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.67,0:28:25.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四年前殺了幾個你們的人
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.43,0:28:27.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  山姆·博斯科和他的小隊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.25,0:28:28.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是他們
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.62,0:28:32.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人曾要我搞到聯調局證件
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.11,0:28:34.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以便他們能進入加調局
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.75,0:28:38.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血腥約翰或者他的手下
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.86,0:28:41.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潛入加調局  對麗貝卡下毒
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.61,0:28:43.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟然為他們提供了幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.57,0:28:46.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時我才知道
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.30,0:28:49.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是在幫助一個連環殺手
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.42,0:28:52.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰讓你搞那些證件的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.63,0:28:55.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道  我只是接到一通電話
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.31,0:28:57.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是組織的運作方式
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.29,0:28:58.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你永遠不知道上線是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.58,0:29:04.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.66,0:29:06.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們能保證我的安全 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.43,0:29:07.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那要看情況了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.38,0:29:11.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你殺害了我的妻子和女兒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.49,0:29:18.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒有殺你的妻子和女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.48,0:29:21.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以我母親的名義起誓
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.47,0:29:32.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你相信他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.95,0:29:34.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他承認了謀殺罪行
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.07,0:29:35.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血腥約翰絕不會這么容易崩潰
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.59,0:29:36.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便是做戲也不會如此
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.60,0:29:38.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果史密斯不是血腥約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.06,0:29:39.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就意味著我們還得繼續追查
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.59,0:29:40.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們需要幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.41,0:29:41.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰是布倫達·夏垂克的繼任者
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.73,0:29:43.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公共關系部嗎  干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.06,0:29:45.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感謝大家能在臨時通知后趕來
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.97,0:29:48.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這位是加調局顧問派翠克·簡
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.63,0:29:50.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他將就血腥約翰一案的進展
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.59,0:29:52.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進行通報
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.76,0:29:55.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.67,0:29:57.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十年前
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.53,0:29:59.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被稱作血腥約翰的連環殺手
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.60,0:30:01.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殺害了我的妻子和女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.56,0:30:05.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自那以后  我們一直在全力追捕他
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.11,0:30:07.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我們很高興地宣布
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.46,0:30:10.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們終于確認了他的身份與面目
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.83,0:30:14.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,執法部門負責人
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.15,0:30:16.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓋爾·伯特侖局長  就是血腥約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.13,0:30:19.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他持有武器  極度危險
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.69,0:30:22.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有人發現他的行蹤  切勿靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.92,0:30:26.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請立即致電加利福尼亞州調查局
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.61,0:30:27.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.61,0:30:37.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請輪流提問
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.90,0:30:45.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉請回避  女士
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.32,0:30:50.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們能談談這事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.53,0:30:52.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.70,0:30:54.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關于伯特侖是血腥約翰的事
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.76,0:30:55.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來就是他
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.38,0:30:59.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果讓簡找到他  簡會殺了他的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.24,0:31:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.64,0:31:03.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們就沒問題嗎  把頂頭上司殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.96,0:31:05.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我無所謂  -我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.53,0:31:07.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.99,0:31:09.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我們保持步調統一
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.26,0:31:11.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是覺得有點詭異
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.13,0:31:22.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伯特侖吸煙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.87,0:31:24.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不吸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.43,0:31:26.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有時候人們會收到打火機作為禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.78,0:31:35.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,范佩爾
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.01,0:31:41.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是個閃存盤
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.90,0:31:42.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們來瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.75,0:31:44.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}納帕谷  七仙女酒廠
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.26,0:31:45.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盤里只有一個文件
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.80,0:31:47.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有密碼保護
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.16,0:31:48.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得硬破解
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.10,0:31:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棒極了  我一直想用用我的新FPGA
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.10,0:31:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}[FPGA: 現場可編程邏輯門排列]
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.93,0:31:52.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的什么
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.02,0:31:54.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我  還是別問了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.21,0:31:56.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\fn方正小标宋_GBK\c&H4E5A72&\fs10\frz-2\pos(213.6,60.167)}加州調查局  內部數據庫
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.50,0:31:59.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.15,0:32:01.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.56,0:32:02.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\fn方正小标宋_GBK\c&H4E5A72&\fs10\frz-2\pos(213.6,60.167)}加州調查局  內部數據庫
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.28,0:32:03.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}[亂碼]
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.46,0:32:06.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該死的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.30,0:32:07.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來像個清單
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.82,0:32:10.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會不會是名單  你能破譯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.19,0:32:11.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.61,0:32:13.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但破解謎題是簡的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.84,0:32:15.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到時候發給他
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.20,0:32:22.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來一杯這個  這種威士忌口感很純
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.75,0:32:23.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用了很多泥煤烘烤麥芽
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.16,0:32:31.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很不錯  能加點冰塊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.92,0:32:34.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你確定嗎  這可是上好的蘇格蘭威士忌
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.27,0:32:37.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我確定
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.30,0:32:50.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙跟你有點像
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.66,0:32:54.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\fn微软雅黑\c&HFCFEFD&\fs16\frz-3\pos(258.6,184.513)}連環殺人犯
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.66,0:32:54.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\i1\c&HDAE0D8&\fs12\frz-1\pos(148.2,184.513)}即時新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.69,0:33:27.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要一輛車
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.07,0:33:36.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們在去酒吧的路上了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.37,0:33:38.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高速巡警封鎖了高速公路
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.07,0:33:39.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要他一跑我們就能抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.46,0:33:40.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他要是躲起來怎么辦
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.68,0:33:42.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伯特侖在柑橘高地殺了個酒保
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.72,0:33:44.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在那邊的姨媽有間房子
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.39,0:33:45.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得他在那里嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.89,0:33:47.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她六個月之前搬到養老院去了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.99,0:33:49.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以她家現在空著
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.51,0:33:51.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽起來是個不錯的藏身之處  地址在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.68,0:33:53.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露絲瑪麗街1408號
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.62,0:33:55.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們就到  讓周和快速反應小組過去
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.91,0:33:57.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備好直升機
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.48,0:34:15.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-他在這嗎  -在那里面
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.23,0:34:16.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我讓卡爾和幾個人去后面了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.60,0:34:18.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-他無處可逃  -我們能信他們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.13,0:34:20.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看了他們的肩膀  沒有紋身
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.60,0:34:26.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你來這里干什么  我沒叫薩城警局派特警
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.43,0:34:27.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人要我們來的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.75,0:34:29.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那邊建一個指揮中心
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.92,0:34:31.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽著  各位  這里由我負責
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.56,0:34:32.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們是從北區來的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.83,0:34:35.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都跨了整個城了  到底是什么情況
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.72,0:34:38.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是他干的  他把他們叫來的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.89,0:34:41.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伯特侖把特警叫到自己這來干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.71,0:34:43.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不止召來了一個特警組
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.33,0:34:45.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他把整個特警隊都召來了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.28,0:34:47.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一片混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.18,0:34:48.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,屋后有整整一隊別的警察在準備
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.62,0:34:50.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們無法控制局面了  頭兒
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.06,0:34:53.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在他們之中  伯特侖混在他們之中
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.08,0:34:55.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他要逃跑  我們得停止行動
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.40,0:34:59.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰都不許走
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.35,0:35:01.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個人都不許走
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.01,0:35:40.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你安全了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.00,0:35:48.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得吃點東西
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.63,0:35:50.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要吃中餐么  我知道有一家很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.82,0:35:53.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  聽起來不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.65,0:36:00.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們在屋里發現了伯特侖的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.33,0:36:02.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該是有人在他去之前
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.10,0:36:03.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在房子里放好了特警服
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.24,0:36:04.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后把城里所有的特警和
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.73,0:36:06.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快速反應小組叫了過去
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.08,0:36:07.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道是誰打的電話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.97,0:36:09.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是個能進行大面積暗箱操縱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.83,0:36:11.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布萊克組織
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.70,0:36:13.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,頭兒
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.96,0:36:16.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請各位注意一下
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.34,0:36:19.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放下電話  離開你們的桌子
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.05,0:36:20.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.85,0:36:23.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是這里特別探員主管特蕾莎·里斯本
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.90,0:36:25.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又是哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.40,0:36:28.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聯調局監管部門探員  丹尼斯·阿爾伯特
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.03,0:36:32.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再說一遍  站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.50,0:36:34.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,離開桌子
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.85,0:36:36.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.31,0:36:38.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們正在追捕
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.38,0:36:40.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一名極其危險的逃犯
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.36,0:36:42.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你們想協助
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.13,0:36:45.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們這個所謂的執法部門的長官
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.45,0:36:46.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是個殺人犯
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.06,0:36:49.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是重大犯罪組織的一員
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.87,0:36:53.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個組織里也有聯調局探員
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.21,0:36:54.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對  所以局里把我
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.93,0:36:56.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從德州奧斯汀調過來
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.02,0:36:58.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收拾你們這個爛攤子
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.82,0:37:05.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我手里有一份
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.20,0:37:08.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聯邦法官簽署的令狀
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.71,0:37:12.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聯調局將立即關停你們部門
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.81,0:37:15.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.72,0:37:18.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解除任職
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.58,0:37:19.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立即生效
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.41,0:37:20.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能這么做
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.56,0:37:24.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是來收集證據的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.64,0:37:25.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要妨礙我
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.80,0:37:27.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大伙開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.90,0:37:47.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.60,0:37:48.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.81,0:37:54.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是聯調局的丹尼斯·阿爾伯特
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.25,0:37:55.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定是派翠克·簡了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.58,0:37:56.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們關停了我們部門
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.84,0:37:58.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們到時候會找你問話
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.73,0:38:00.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過可以緩一緩  我們會在這兒待一陣子
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.75,0:38:02.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別出城
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.95,0:38:05.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們還有個兇手要抓
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.38,0:38:07.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這案子現在歸我們管了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.13,0:38:09.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有過機會  但是搞砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.17,0:38:10.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你當時是真想抓他的話
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.94,0:38:22.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我最喜歡的杯子
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.05,0:38:29.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  幸會  再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.79,0:38:36.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在怎么辦
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.92,0:38:39.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.03,0:38:41.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,范佩爾在伯特侖的閃存里找到了一些加密文件
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.82,0:38:42.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們要不要從那開始查
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.89,0:38:45.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了  浪費時間而已  結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.76,0:38:47.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這里沒我們的事兒了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.58,0:38:50.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回家吧  休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.04,0:38:53.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不會放棄  我不信你會放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.98,0:38:56.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我不是放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.22,0:39:00.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是放手
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.87,0:39:04.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前的情況我們已經無法掌控了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.96,0:39:07.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保持聯絡  好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.11,0:39:11.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的一切  我很抱歉
